{"results":[{"aya":"050","id":3838,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"于是他们走向前来，互相谈论。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"051","id":3839,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他们中有一个人说：我有一个朋友，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"052","id":3840,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他问我：'你确是诚信的吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"053","id":3841,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"难道我们死后，已变为尘土和朽骨的时候，还必定要受报酬吗？'","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"054","id":3842,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他说：你们愿看他吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"055","id":3843,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他俯视下面，就看见他在火狱的中央，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"056","id":3844,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他说：以真主发誓，你的确几乎陷害了我。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":26,"previousPage":"/zh/s037-7.json","nextPage":"/zh/s037-9.json"}}